ition":0},"title":"Hadith on Sincerity: Good will protects from hatred, malice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are three traits by which a believer will have no malice: sincerity in deeds for Allah, goodwill to the Muslims, and uniting with their community.\" Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 1279 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi\u00a0(authentic\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32491,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/world-is-cursed-except-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":24317,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Entire world cursed but sincerity to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe world is cursed and everything in it is cursed, except whatever seeks the countenance of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 602 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37869,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/tawhid-ikhlas-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24317,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Whoever worships Allah sincerely enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says there is no God but Allah sincerely, he will be admitted into Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Du\u2019a\u0304\u2019 li-T\u0323abara\u0304ni 1478 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5868,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/03\/virtue-swallow-anger\/","url_meta":{"origin":24317,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Great virtue of controlling, swallowing anger","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is nothing swallowed with a greater reward from Allah than a servant who swallows his rage, seeking thereby the countenance of Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4189 Grade:\u00a0Sahih li ghayrihi\u00a0(authentic due to external evidence) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/acts-of-worship-spoiled\/","url_meta":{"origin":24317,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Worship: Acts of worship spoiled by insincerity and sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne who fasts might only acquire hunger and thirst from his fasting. One who stands for prayer might only acquire fatigue from his prayer.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 13413 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2578,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/28\/ask-allah-alone-for-needs\/","url_meta":{"origin":24317,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Let one of you ask Allah for all of his needs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLet one of you ask his Lord for his needs, all of them, even for a shoestring when his breaks.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3973 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u063